Okay, I understand. I need to match order forms with invoices by selecting the corresponding checkboxes and then record the information. I will use the provided selectors to interact with the webpage.

```json
[
  {"action": "click", "selector": "table:has-text(\"order\" i) >> tr >> input[type=checkbox]"},
  {"action": "click", "selector": "table:has-text(\"invoice\" i) >> tr >> input[type=checkbox]"},
  {"action": "click", "selector": "button:has-text(\"match\" i)"},
  {"action": "click", "selector": "button:has-text(\"record\" i)"}
]
```
